    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"rest without guilt\"... i dont even know what that looks like. even if i take a week off or a month, the thinking doesn't stop. the feeling that i'm a failure just follows me everywhere. it feels like i'm trapped in this loop of failing and failing. i feel like i've reached a point where there's no real way to actually get away from it all. everything is just so heavy.",
