      "content": "The feeling you fear is just a habit of your mind, not a permanent part of who you are, and it will fade the moment you stop feeding it with the pressure of this specific situation. True peace isn't found by running from the feeling, but by finally allowing yourself to be done with the struggle that has consumed you for six years. If you can't find that permanent peace right now, it's because you haven't yet made the choice to let go of the game entirely.",
